      <title>Super proud of this loooong mural I just completed for Carlton Hills Elementary ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DIp8ehdOZHn/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/491444252_18502344574024351_6181213661355583549_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=MzYxNDY4NjE1NjI0MDI5NDM3NTE4NTAyMzQ0NTY4MDI0MzUx.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjI0MTB4NDI4NC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=10qfOTzNosMQ7kNvwFd72iz&amp;_nc_oc=AdqqcuaDu9d_VyefmsYN1IPM4R0RHII0y2M2iwDszOTFP47ci50gyhVHiUS9xSVzLac&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DK6iweAx95QZ5Jos7G1kKw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwNcEj4iW0sHLSWHqgCr8-_FVzoRwQwE6ru8wP-bCm-gg&amp;oe=69C90323" alt="Instagram billede fra @katyyeaw" /></p><p><strong>@katyyeaw</strong></p><p>Super proud of this loooong mural I just completed for Carlton Hills Elementary School in Santee, California. <br/>
<br/>
The school hired me to do one mural over the summer, and they liked it so much they got a grant for me to do two more.  Here is the end result- the entire courtyard and lunch area are surrounded by art! <br/>
<br/>
Their mascot is the jaguar so I decided to paint a serene landscape with sweet jaguars lounging around.  A giant “welcome to Carlton Hills” greets you as you enter the school.  I think it came out pretty awesome!<br/>
<br/>
I’m so grateful for my amazing painting assistants (who are all fellow artists ) - @mrmrsir @kcaughey @marytheartfullyogi @stuffmarydoes</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/491444252_18502344574024351_6181213661355583549_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=MzYxNDY4NjE1NjI0MDI5NDM3NTE4NTAyMzQ0NTY4MDI0MzUx.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjI0MTB4NDI4NC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=10qfOTzNosMQ7kNvwFd72iz&amp;_nc_oc=AdqqcuaDu9d_VyefmsYN1IPM4R0RHII0y2M2iwDszOTFP47ci50gyhVHiUS9xSVzLac&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DK6iweAx95QZ5Jos7G1kKw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwNcEj4iW0sHLSWHqgCr8-_FVzoRwQwE6ru8wP-bCm-gg&amp;oe=69C90323" alt="Instagram billede fra @katyyeaw" /></p><p><strong>@katyyeaw</strong></p><p>Super proud of this loooong mural I just completed for Carlton Hills Elementary School in Santee, California. <br/>
<br/>
The school hired me to do one mural over the summer, and they liked it so much they got a grant for me to do two more.  Here is the end result- the entire courtyard and lunch area are surrounded by art! <br/>
<br/>
Their mascot is the jaguar so I decided to paint a serene landscape with sweet jaguars lounging around.  A giant “welcome to Carlton Hills” greets you as you enter the school.  I think it came out pretty awesome!<br/>
<br/>
I’m so grateful for my amazing painting assistants (who are all fellow artists ) - @mrmrsir @kcaughey @marytheartfullyogi @stuffmarydoes</p>]]></content:encoded>
